<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0-alpha.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-y3tfxAZXuh4HwSYylfB+J125MxIs6mR5FOHamPBG064zB+AFeWH94NdvaCBm8qnd" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">

    <link href="~/Scripts/Style.css" rel="stylesheet" />

    <style>
        .navbar {
            background-color: white !important;
        }


        .hero-image {
            background-image: url('../../Content/Images/parentsplastic.JPG');
            height: 50%;
            background-position: center;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-size: cover;
            position: relative;
            width:100%;
         
        }
        .btn {
            font-family: 'Comic Sans MS';
            width: 200px;
        }

        hr {
  margin-top: 0rem;
  margin-bottom: 0rem;
  border: 0;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  width:50%;
}




        .imgsize {
            height: 240px;
            width: 180px;
        }

        .card-container {
            perspective: 500rem;
            position: relative;
            height: 291.6px;
            margin: 20px;
            width:0px;
        }

        .card-front, .card-back {
            -webkit-backface-visibility: hidden;
            backface-visibility: hidden;
            -webkit-transition: 0.6s;
            transition: 0.6s;
            -webkit-transform-style: preserve-3d;
            transform-style: preserve-3d;
        }

        .card-front {
            background-color: #F0F8FF;
            z-index: 2;
            -webkit-transform: rotateY(0deg);
            transform: rotateY(0deg);
        }

        .card-container:hover .card-front {
            transform: rotateY(180deg);
        }

        .card-container:hover .card-back {
            transform: rotateY(0deg);
        }

        .card-back {
            background-color: #F0F8FF;
            -webkit-transform: rotateY(-180deg);
            transform: rotateY(-180deg);
        }


        .card {
            transition: 0.8s all;
            position: absolute;
            height: 100%;
            width: 100%;
            backface-visibility: hidden;
            
            left: 20%;
            margin: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #555;
        }

        .card-back .card-body {
            position: relative;
        }


       
    </style>

</head>

<body>


    <div class="hero-image" style="height:550px">
        <div class="hero-text" style="text-align:center;transform: translate(-50%, -50%); position:absolute;left:50%;top:50%;">

            <h2 style="color:white;font-family:'Comic Sans MS'">
                In Australia, on an average 130,000 tons of plastic <br /> is decomposed into the ocean per year.
            </h2>
           
            <a href="#solution" class="btn btn-primary center-block" style="margin-top: 30px;">
                <i class="fa fa-cog fa-spin"></i>  Save our Earth!
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>


    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class="col-md-3"></div>
            <div class="col-md-3">
                <video width="350" height="260" autoplay muted loop style="margin-top:10px;">
                    <source src="~/Content/Images/plasticbag.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
                </video>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3">
                <p style="margin-top:60px;font-family:'Comic Sans MS'">
                    <b> Did you know?</b><br>Recent Greenpeace analysis found that Australians alone use over 9.7 billion single-use
                    plastic bags annually.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3"></div>

        </div>

    </div>
    <hr />

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class="col-md-3"></div>
            <div class="col-md-3">
                <p style="margin-top:60px;font-family:'Comic Sans MS'">
                    <b> Poor Animals</b><br>In Australia, 90% of all seabirds living today eat some kind of plastic.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3" style="text-align:right;">
                <video width="350" height="260" autoplay muted loop style="margin-top:10px;">
                    <source src="~/Content/Images/seabirds2.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
                </video>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3"></div>


        </div>

    </div>
    <hr />
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class="col-md-3"></div>
            <div class="col-md-3">
                <video width="350" height="260" autoplay muted loop style="margin-top:10px;">
                    <source src="~/Content/Images/challenge.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
                </video>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3">
                <p style="margin-top:60px;font-family:'Comic Sans MS'">
                    <b> The Challenge</b><br>The adolescents of Australia are concerned about the plastic pollution issue but are
                    unsure how to deal with it since there aren't enough platforms to guide them in the
                    right direction.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3"></div>

        </div>

    </div>
    <div id="solution" style="background-color:azure;margin:5px;">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12" style="text-align:center;">
                <p style="font-family:'Comic Sans MS';font-size:1.25em;">
                    <b>PlaBOO</b><br />
                    Suggests possible alternatives for the common plastic items in an entertaining
                    manner, entertain users with quizzes and show the nearby recycling centers.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12" style="text-align:center;">
                <div class="col-md-3"></div>
                <div class="col-md-3 center-block" style="margin-bottom:10px;">
                    <div class="card-container">
                        <div class="card card-front" style="width:15rem;">
                            <div class="inner">
                                <img src="~/Content/Images/Alternative1.jpg" class="card-img-top imgsize center" alt="Missing img">
                            </div>
                            <div class="card-body">

                                <span style="margin-left:15px;" class="glyphicon glyphicon-refresh"></span>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="card card-back" style="width:15rem;">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <p style="font-family:'Comic Sans MS'">
                                    By clicking on this tile, you will be able to see the plastic alternatives
                                    for the items you use daily.
                                </p>


                            </div>
                        </div>

                    </div>
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary flip" style="margin-left: -30px; margin-top: 0px;"
                            onclick="location.href='@Url.Action("Index", "Alternatives")'">
                        Alternatives
                    </button>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3 center-block" style="margin-bottom:10px;">
                    <div class="card-container">
                        <div class="card card-front" style="width:15rem;">
                            <div class="inner">
                                <img src="~/Content/Images/quiz1.jpg" class="card-img-top imgsize center" alt="Missing img">
                            </div>
                            <div class="card-body">

                                <span style="margin-left:15px;" class="glyphicon glyphicon-refresh"></span>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="card card-back" style="width:15rem;">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <p style="font-family:'Comic Sans MS'">
                                    Interesting quizzes to check your understanding of how plastic affects
                                    the environment.
                                </p>


                            </div>
                        </div>

                    </div>
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary flip" style="margin-left: -30px; margin-top: 0px;"
                            onclick="location.href='@Url.Action("Index", "Alternatives")'">
                        Quiz
                    </button>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3"></div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>